{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第十五回 箭神的神箭\n班察巴那以五箭试探小方，证明其无辜。驼子被无名剑客重伤，临死指认凶手。小方在黑色鹰羽帐篷发现波娃与卜鹰，卜鹰竟是鹰记商队东主。班察巴那指控波娃是杀人凶手，小方坚信其无辜。卜鹰让波娃离开，但要求小方留下作为交换。小方与波娃告别，承诺将来寻找她。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "两种法子，你选哪一种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你已经可以开始数了，最好数得快一点，我最怕久等。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一、二、三、四……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你总该相信了，一个无辜的人，是绝不会被冤杀的。\n\n只要你无辜，这五枝箭就绝对射不到你身上，不管我是不是五花箭神都一样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "原来你也有点害怕的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "不是有一点害怕。我怕得要命。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我知道你有话要告诉我。你一定要说出来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到……想不到……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "想不到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到杀人的竟是他。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他是什么人？到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我也想不到是你，我一直都认为你真的从不杀人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "世上本来就有很多令人想不到的事，金子可以让人做出很多很多连他自己都想不到的事来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我知道你也在找那批金子，可是你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "带我走，求求你带我走吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "我一定会带你走，你本就不该来的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "你怎么会来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不知道，我真的不知道，我只想赶快走。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她不能走。谁也不能带她走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为要别人流血的人，自己也得流血。杀人者死，以血还血。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你应该看得出杀人的不是她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你看得出？你看出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们这些人，这些货物，都是属于一个商家的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "哪一个商家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "鹰记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "鹰记？飞鹰的鹰？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你就是他们的东主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们收容你，就因为他是我们的东主，我们信任你，也是因为他，否则你刚才很可能已死在我的箭下。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就算他要搜索那批黄金，也不会搜到他自己的队伍中来，就算他要搜查这批货，也用不着杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经应该知道杀人的是谁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "我只知道杀人的绝不是她。谁也没有看见杀人的是谁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你一定要亲眼看见杀人的是谁？你一定要亲眼看见才相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就算他真的亲眼看见了，也不会相信的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有人看见她杀人，没有人能证明她杀过人。可是你也同样不能证明她是无辜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你是不是又想用刚才那法子证明？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。五花箭神的箭，绝不会伤及无辜的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "只可惜你并不是真的五花箭神，你只不过是个人，你心里已认定了她有罪。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这次你是不是还有什么更好的法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你虽然说过，只要你活着，就不让别人欺负我，可是我早就知道这是做不到的，每件事都会改变，每个人都会改变。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以现在你已经可以忘记这些话，就让他们杀了我，就让我死吧！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让她走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "就这么样放她走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "不是这么样放她走。你还得给她一袋水、一袋食粮、一匹马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "最快的一匹马，我要让她走得越快越好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她走，你留下。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我留下？你要我留下？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你要我放她走，你就得留下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "这是条件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "只要我不死，我一定会去找你，一定能找到你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    }
  ],
